_sText:
gg sky arena max

This is a medium sized map with very fast game play that takes place in a 3d open maze.  The map has three levels of play.  Buy Zones are included.  There are 4 Teleporters available to make getting around quick and easy. Gravity is set to HALF of normal in order to make the game play awesome. Enjoy!

Watch In 1080p!
<iframe width="640" height="390" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/aJu-pH6DkDA" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

-	64 spawn points, 32 per team
-	Nav file for bots
-	Buy Zones
-	Custom skybox texture by Komaokc
